    <h2>Our Story</h2>
    <p class="text-large">Hunt Logic AI started in 2024 when a group of software engineers and lifelong hunters got tired of spending hours sorting trail camera photos and guessing when to hunt. We knew there had to be a better way.</p>

    <p class="text-large">What started as a weekend project to automatically identify deer in trail camera photos evolved into a comprehensive AI platform used by over 50,000 hunters across North America.</p>

    <h2 class="mt-3">Our Mission</h2>
    <p class="text-large">We believe hunting should be about the experience - the time in nature, the tradition, the connection to the outdoors. Not endless hours of photo sorting and guesswork.</p>

    <p class="text-large">Our mission is to give every hunter the tools to succeed while preserving the essence of what makes hunting meaningful. Technology should make you a better hunter, not replace the hunt itself.</p>

    <h2 class="mt-3">Conservation Commitment</h2>
    <p class="text-large">Ethical hunting and conservation go hand-in-hand. Hunt Logic AI partners with wildlife conservation organizations and contributes 1% of revenue to habitat preservation and wildlife research.</p>

    <p class="text-large">Better hunting data helps wildlife managers make informed decisions. Improved success rates mean less wounding loss and more ethical harvests.</p>

